resources.description: Search for user activities in the CRM system using the provided OData search expression. The search expression maps to the OData $filter clause. For example, to search for all activities with type Meeting', the search expression parameter will be mapped from where: type=‘Meeting’ to $filter: type eq Meeting. If a search expression is not provided, then the first 150 records will be returned. Only returns details about your account.

resources.description: Find the contacts in the CRM system, using the given, optional CEQL search expression. The search expression maps to the OData $filter clause. For example, to search for all contacts whose last name is ‘smith', the search expression parameter will be mapped from where: lastName=‘smith’ to $filter: lastName eq smith. If a search expression is not provided, then the first 150 records will be returned. Only returns details about your account.
